%% Process Flow - Agent Monitoring Pipeline
sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as AI Agent Session
    participant Hooks as Lifecycle Hooks
    participant Server as Monitoring Service
    participant Dashboard as Real-time Dashboard
    participant App as Desktop Companion
    participant Dev as Developer

    Note over Agent,Dev: Agent Session Lifecycle

    Agent->>Hooks: Session begins
    activate Hooks
    Hooks->>Server: Register agent (non-blocking)
    deactivate Hooks
    activate Server
    Server->>Server: Store in agent registry
    Server-->>Dashboard: Broadcast: new agent online
    Server-->>App: Telemetry update available
    deactivate Server

    activate Dashboard
    Dashboard-->>Dev: Dashboard shows new agent
    deactivate Dashboard
    activate App
    App-->>Dev: Notification: agent started
    deactivate App

    loop Every Heartbeat Interval
        Agent->>Hooks: Tool use / progress event
        Hooks->>Server: Heartbeat + metrics
        Server-->>Dashboard: Live metric update
        Server-->>App: Updated telemetry
    end

    Note over Agent,Dev: Formation Deployment (Multi-Agent)

    Dev->>Server: Deploy agent formation
    activate Server
    Server->>Server: Create formation, assign roles
    Server-->>Dashboard: Formation topology rendered
    Server-->>App: Formation status update
    deactivate Server

    loop Formation Agents Active
        Agent->>Hooks: Wave progress / completion
        Hooks->>Server: Status + dependency update
        Server-->>Dashboard: Formation graph updates
    end

    Agent->>Hooks: Session ends
    Hooks->>Server: Deregister agent
    Server-->>Dashboard: Agent marked complete
    Server-->>App: Session summary available
    App-->>Dev: Final metrics delivered
